  "original_title": "\u0db4\u0dd9\u0da7\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dbd\u0dca , \u0da9\u0dd3\u0dc3\u0dbd\u0dca \u0dc4\u0dcf \u0d9c\u0dd1\u0dc3\u0dca \u0db1\u0dd0\u0dc0\u0dca \u0d91\u0db1 \u0daf\u0dd2\u0db1 \u0dc3\u0dc4 \u0dbb\u0da7\u0dda \u0d89\u0db1\u0dca\u0db0\u0db1 \u0dc3\u0d82\u0da0\u0dd2\u0dad \u0d9c\u0dd0\u0db1 \u0d85\u0d9c\u0db8\u0dd0\u0dad\u0dd2\u0d9c\u0dda \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dc1\u0dda\u0dc2 \u0db4\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dc1\u0dba",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Special Statement by the Prime Minister on the arrival dates of petrol, diesel and gas ships and the country's fuel reserves",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe made a special statement on Wednesday (June 14) regarding the arrival dates of petrol, diesel and gas ships and the country's existing fuel reserves.",
        "He said that if fuel was distributed on a 50% basis, fuel could be supplied continuously and the existing stocks would be sufficient for the next seven days only.",
        "The Prime Minister also explained how to resolve the fuel crisis as well as how to work with foreign countries to resolve the country's economic crisis."
      ],
